cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with image segmentation using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a unique attention module and recurrent processing also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) data and digital phantoms suggests a potential focus on neuroscience (cs.NE) or multimedia (cs.MM).
